to be an effective epidemic control measure, especially for cholera. - MPP
The comment is perhaps too guarded. It should say that quarantine is not
an effective ..."
Also, the actions reported to have been taken are in violation of the
International Health Regulations. China can petition the Director General
of WHO to intercede.
